Slaughter got a mouthful of Motormaster's fist, but his armour was far
to strong for Slaughter to actually bite through. "I'm the most endurant
thing on the road organic. I'll make you the flattest thing on the
road." he threatened, as he grabbed with his one fist not in Slaughter,
and reached around behind his neck.
